channel.title: TSM Presque Isle
channel.description:
The Townsquare Media Presque Isle Podcast features local artists and musicians from Northern Maine and Western New Brunswick. If you're a local artist and would like to be part of the podcast send an email to josh.archer@townsquaremedia.com. Make sure to include links to your work so we can check out your awesomeness.
Visit the wonderful Townsquare Media Presque Isle websites to keep track of the goings on in Northern Maine and Western New Brunswick: http://q961.com, http://bigcountry969.com, http://1019therock.com.
